// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0005 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 086aa174-9898-5ef4-933a-f70a43e02d75

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:1*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
